image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Noah-Kahan.-CREDIT_-Jason-Kempin_Getty-Images-for-Pilgrimage-Music-Cultural-Festival.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Noah-Kahan.-CREDIT_-Jason-Kempin_Getty-Images-for-Pilgrimage-Music-Cultural-Festival-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Noah-Kahan.-CREDIT_-Jason-Kempin_Getty-Images-for-Pilgrimage-Music-Cultural-Festival-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Noah-Kahan.-CREDIT_-Jason-Kempin_Getty-Images-for-Pilgrimage-Music-Cultural-Festival-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Noah-Kahan.-CREDIT_-Jason-Kempin_Getty-Images-for-Pilgrimage-Music-Cultural-Festival-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Noah-Kahan.-CREDIT_-Jason-Kempin_Getty-Images-for-Pilgrimage-Music-Cultural-Festival-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noah-kahan">诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan)</a>已被宣布成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/british-summer-time-bst-festival">BST 海德公园</a>2025 年的主角 - 您可以在下面找到所有详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/noah-kahan-in-london-setlist-photos-3587843">诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan) 在伦敦：崛起的民谣流行巨星走向舞台</a></strong></li></ul><p>这将成为这位民谣流行歌手迄今为止在英国最大的头条秀，他将于 7 月 5 日星期五登上舞台。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">格雷西·艾布拉姆斯 (Gracie Abrams)</a>也将加入他的行列，阵容中的更多名字尚未公布。</p><p>门票于本周五（11 月 8 日）上午 10 点（格林尼治标准时间）开始发售，可<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Famerican-express-presents-bst-hyde-park-tickets%2Fartist%2F1842565" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买。另外，Amex 客户可以从格林尼治标准时间今天（11 月 4 日）上午 10:00 开始进行预售。</p><p> Kahan 是继<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jeff-lynne">Jeff Lynne</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/electric-light-orchestra">ELO</a>将于明年在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/british-summer-time-bst-festival">海德公园</a>举行告别演出并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jeff-lynnes-elo-announces-farewell-show-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2025-buy-tickets-3804580">将于 7 月 13 日星期日在 Great Oak 舞台上演出的</a>消息之后，第四位被揭晓的 2025 年头条新闻。它将跟随他们的“Over And Out”美国巡演，并将作为对歌迷的最后“告别”。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">我们很高兴宣布<a href="https://twitter.com/NoahKahan?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@NoahKahan</a>将成为美国运通明年夏天呈献<a href="https://twitter.com/BSTHydePark?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@BSTHydePark</a>的头条新闻<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2600.png" alt="☀" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p><p>特邀嘉宾<a href="https://twitter.com/gracieabrams?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@gracieabrams</a>将于 2025 年 7 月 4 日星期五在伦敦海德公园与他会面，完整阵容即将公布！ </p><p><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f39f.png" alt="🎟" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" />美国运通卡会员可以… <a href="https://t.co/xj4XRZJfyS">pic.twitter.com/xj4XRZJfyS</a></p><p> - BST 海德公园 (@BSTHydePark) <a href="https://twitter.com/BSTHydePark/status/1853361607985799589?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 11 月 4 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p>美国乡村音乐明星<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zach-bryan">扎克·布莱恩 (Zach Bryan)</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-3806223">被宣布成为头条新闻</a>，并将于 6 月 28 日至 29 日在大橡树舞台 (Great Oak Stage) 上演，后者是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/zach-bryan-adds-extra-london-show-at-bst-hyde-park-2025-due-to-phenomenal-demand-buy-tickets-3808323">由于“巨大的需求”而增加的</a>一场额外演出。</p><p>上周，休<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hugh-jackman">·杰克曼 (Hugh Jackman)</a>也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hugh-jackman-announced-as-bst-hyde-park-2025-headliner-get-tickets-3808633">加入了演出阵容，并将于 7 月 6 日星期日表演英国独家演出《来自伦敦的爱》(From London with Love)。</a>在该节目中，他将演唱音乐剧中的歌曲，包括<em>《绿野仙踪》</em> 、 <em>《马戏之王》</em> 、 <em>《悲惨世界》</em>和<em>《音乐人</em>》以及其他惊喜。</p><p> BST 海德公园 2024 的主角包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-stevie-nicks-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-3765318">Stevie Nicks</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kylie-minogue-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-london-stage-times-3774511">Kylie Minogue</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/special-guests-announced-for-stray-kids-london-bst-hyde-park-show-3763729">Stray Kids</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-sza-at-bst-hyde-park-2024-3760887">SZA</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/more-support-acts-added-to-kings-of-leons-london-bst-hyde-park-2024-show-3762832">Kings Of Leon</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morgan-wallen-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3598527">Morgan Wallen</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hans-zimmer-seal-and-more-announced-as-special-guests-for-andrea-bocelli-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3763248">Andrea Bocelli</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/robbie-williams-to-headline-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-buy-tickets-3553493">Robbie Williams</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/full-line-up-announced-for-shania-twain-at-londons-bst-hyde-park-2024-3764110">Shania Twain</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3783578" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3783578" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3783578" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Noah-Kahan-live@2000x1270.jpg" alt="诺亚·卡汉 (Noah Kahan) 将于 2024 年演出。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Noah-Kahan-live@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Noah-Kahan-live@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Noah-Kahan-live@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 8